Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:03.85,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,My name is Amana Osaki, and I'm 17 years old.\N大崎あまな 17歳です
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:08.61,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,If I'm chosen as the cover \Ngirl for your magazine,\Nもし 恩師のカバーガールに決まったら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.07,0:00:13.43,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,I want to share its appeal with \Nas many people as possible!\N恩師の魅力を たくさんの人に届けたいと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.15,0:00:18.73,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Amana-chan... You're accepted!\N天菜ちゃん 合格
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.73,0:00:20.61,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Huh? Already?!\Nえっ?もう?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:23.64,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah! Perfect!\Nう うん 完璧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.64,0:00:27.85,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,No way! I want you to be tougher on me!\N嘘だ もっと厳しくお願いしたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:31.42,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so... Well then...\Nそ そっか じゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:38.76,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,It's empty. I don't feel \Nanything from you at all!\N空っぽですね 何も感じません
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.25,0:00:43.75,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,Chiyuki-san?\Nちひゆきさん?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.08,0:00:46.86,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,It's just a little game of \Nopposites, Tenka-chan.\N反対ごっこよ 天下ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.93,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,Opposites... game?\N反対 ごっこ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.93,0:00:53.84,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,If you think of it as saying the \Nopposite of what you really feel,\N思ってるのと反対のことを言う遊びだと思えば
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:55.42,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,even harsh words can be easier to handle!\Nきついことだって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.19,0:01:03.70,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,Uh, your greetings... are kinda weak!\N挨拶のキレが イマイチです
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.94,0:01:09.00,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Besides, Osaki-san, you're busy \Nwith Alstroemeria too, right?\Nそれに 大崎さんはアルストロメリアとしてもお忙しいですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.72,0:01:11.51,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,You can't fool me.\Nごまかせませんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.51,0:01:16.86,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Can you really give us your all \Nwhile preparing for the album and tour?\Nアルバムやツアーの準備をしながら うちのために頑張れるんですか?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:20.97,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,I'll do my best! I'll see \Neverything through to the end!\N頑張ります 全部しっかりやり遂げます!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:25.24,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,Y-You're accepted!\Nご 合格!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.91,0:01:28.73,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Huh?! Wait, was that part \Nof the opposites game?\Nうえっ って反対ごっこ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.07,0:01:33.32,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,That... was a for-reals game!\N今のは 本当ごっこ です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:37.23,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Geez, you're spoiling me too much!\Nもう あまなを甘やかしすぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:43.06,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,But I understand. \NYou want to be well-prepared.\Nでもちゃんと準備したいのは分かるな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.94,0:01:47.87,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,We also need to research that magazine \Nand come up with a plan, right?\Nその雑誌のこともリサーチして 対策しなきゃね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:55.09,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Yeah! It's a new magazine, I think it's \Ncalled something like "{\i1}Apricot{\i0}"...\Nうん 新しい雑誌らしいんだけど アプリコットみたいな名前で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.37,0:01:54.25,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,What?\Nえっ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:01:59.94,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait... maybe it's not new,\N it could be a reissue.\Nあれ 新しいんじゃなくて 復刊だったかも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:04.13,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,Chiyuki-san?\Nちゆきさん?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.62,0:02:07.49,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Ah, n-no, it's nothing!\Nあっ ううん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:04:00.38,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,I used to read it thoroughly... \Nthe special feature in {\i1}Apricot{\i0}.\Nよく読んだなあ アプリコットの特集
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:03.72,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,I just love it.\N大好き
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:10.39,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Thank you for helping us out so much.\Nありがとう こんなに手伝ってくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:14.27,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,It takes all three of us to \Nmake Alstroemeria, right?\N3人でアルストロメリアでしょ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:17.90,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's aim for the Grand Prix!\Nうん 目指せ グランプリ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.91,0:04:23.47,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'll work hard, thinking \Nof us all being there together!\Nうん アマナ みんなで出ると思って頑張るね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:29.02,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,If it's Amana-chan... \NI'm certain it'll be wonderful.\Nアマナちゃんなら 素敵だよね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:33.14,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,How nice...\Nいいな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:57.74,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,Wow, Na-chan, you're amazing! So good!\Nすごい なあちゃん すごい上手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:01.46,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Practicing your walking?\Nウォーキングの練習?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:04.52,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Ah, Chiyuki-san! Yeah!\Nあ 千雪さん うん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:10.00,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to learn from an instructor, \Nbut I have to practice on my own, too.\N専門の先生にも習うんだけど 自分でもやっとかなきゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:14.83,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,But, you know, it's really hard to \Nget a booking with the instructor...\Nでもね 先生の予約がなかなか取れないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:17.96,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,I think I can get one the day after tomorrow,\N but we don't have a place to practice.\N明後日は撮れそうなんだけど 場所がなくて…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:23.74,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,The day after tomorrow... Oh, because I\Nalready reserved this place.\N明後日…私がここを予約しちゃってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:26.13,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Ah, no, that's not what I meant!\Nあっ ううん そういうことじゃないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:27.59,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,B-but...\Nで でも
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:32.66,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.\Nごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:38.11,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,No, no, I'm the one who \Nsaid something weird...\Nううん 天菜こそ変なこと言っちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.40,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Oh, right, here!\Nあっ そうだ これ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:50.47,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,I thought it might be helpful \Nfor your studies, if you'd like.\Nあのね よかったらお勉強用にって思って
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:56.63,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Wow, is this {\i1}Apricot{\i0}? \NChiyuki-san, you had this on hand?\Nあっ これアプリコット ちゆきさん持ってたの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:06:01.61,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,No, I just found it at a \Nused bookstore yesterday.\Nううん たまたま 昨日 古本屋さんで見つけて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:03.73,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,It's so cute!\Nかわいい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:07.72,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's such... such \Na wonderful magazine...\Nうん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:13.19,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's such... such \Na wonderful magazine...\Nすっごく すっごくすてきな雑誌なの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:16.93,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,Chiyuki-san...\Nちゆきさん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:23.27,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Thank you, Chiyuki-san. \NI'll study really hard!\Nありがとう ちゆきさん あまなめっちゃ勉強するから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:24.70,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Um-hum.\Nうん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:39.96,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,The three of us are Alstroemeria...\N3人で アルストロメリア
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:45.68,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,It's just my own practice session...\N私 ただの自主練なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:51.69,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Hey...\Nねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:52.77,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,\Nうん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:07:00.45,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,You know, Chiyuki-san... do you \Nthink she might really like {\i1}Apricot{\i0}?\Nあのね 千雪さんって もしかして アプリコット
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:03.78,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,I thought so too. It seems like... \Nshe really likes it a lot...\Nてんかも 思った
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.78,0:07:08.69,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,I thought so too. It seems like... \Nshe really likes it a lot...\Nとっても好きだったりするのかもって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:17.91,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,I wonder why... me...\N何でだろう 私
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:23.20,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Why did it have to be {\i1}Apricot{\i0}?\N何で アプリコットなんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.09,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,This is the last one...\Nしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:31.48,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,This is the last one...\Nこれで 最後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:34.38,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,Good wor—\Nお疲れさ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:36.95,SC_Bottom,制作人,0,0,0,,Could we possibly \Nreschedule the meeting again?\Nもう一度 お打ち合わせの時間をいただけませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:42.29,SC_Bottom,制作人,0,0,0,,No, but the idea that the Grand Prix has\N already been decided in favor of Osaki is...\Nいや ですが グランプリが大崎に内定してるっていうのは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:48.90,SC_Bottom,制作人,0,0,0,,It's an honor, but...\Nとても光栄なことではあるんですが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:13.62,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,When the three of us are together, \Nour voices are unbeatable!\N3人揃ったら 最強の声だね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:15.32,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Yeah!\Nうん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:20.49,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Ahh!\Nああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああああ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:19.77,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,Wh-what's wrong?!\N补
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:24.48,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,M-my stomach growled!\Nお お腹になっちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:29.10,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,Na-chan... are you hungry?\Nなあちゃん お腹空いてるの?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:31.60,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Here, take this.\Nじゃあ これ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:36.37,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Wow, really?!\Nあっ いいの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:42.33,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Of course. Right now, you need \Nall the energy you can get.\Nうん あまなちゃん 今は運とエネルギー使わないといけないんだもん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:44.51,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,You should do your best for the audition.\Nオーディション頑張らなきゃね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:50.15,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Yeah, thank you... I'll do my best!\Nうん ありがとう 頑張るね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:53.49,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Oh, speaking of caramel, that reminds me—\Nあっ キャラメルで思い出したんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:56.37,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,there's this super cute flavored \Nlatte that just came out!\Nめっちゃかわいいフレーバーラテが出てたの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.17,0:08:59.35,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Oh, r-really?\Nそ そうなの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:01.97,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'll get one for you tomorrow!\Nうん 明日買ってくるね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:06.92,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Thank you, that sounds really wonderful...\Nありがとう それはすっごく素敵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:10.63,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,but... um, remember to make \Ngood use of your time...\Nだけど あの 時間を大事にして
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:13.82,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,and take care of yourself too, okay?\N自分のことも考えなきゃ ね?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:17.57,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Y-you're right.\Nそ そうだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:20.12,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm sorry...\Nあ あの ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:21.61,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to sound preachy.\N偉そうなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.48,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,No, you're absolutely right!\Nううん その通りだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:25.58,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,I'm the one who should apologize...\Nアマナがごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:27.59,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,N-no, there's no need to apologize.\Nううん ごめんだなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:39.39,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,This is my fault...\Nアマナのせいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:42.60,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,This is my fault.\N私のせい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:46.22,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,I'm overthinking it and \Nmaking things weird.\N気にしすぎて変な感じにしちゃってる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:51.84,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Chiyuki-san is just trying to support me.\N千雪さん アマナのこと応援してくれてるだけなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:55.78,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,She probably realizes... \Nthat I'm being strange...\Nきっと 分かっちゃってるよね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:58.55,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,She probably realizes... \Nthat I'm being strange...\N私 変だもん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:10:02.79,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,Na-chan... Chiyuki-san... \NI... can't do anything...\Nなーちゃん 千ゆきさん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:06.08,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,Na-chan... Chiyuki-san... \NI... can't do anything...\Nてんか 何にも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:10.50,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,The three of us, as Alstroemeria...\N3人で アルストロメリア
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:34.28,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,\Nああああああああああああああああああああ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:38.28,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,\Nああああああああああああああああああああ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:44.30,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,\Nああああああああああああああああああああ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:49.22,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,\Nああああああああああああああああああああ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:05.13,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,It's mom and the others.\Nママ達だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:11.08,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,N-no.\Nあっ うううん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:22.32,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Sorry for showing up at \Nthis hour unannounced.\Nごめんなさい 遅くに突然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:24.74,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,No, it's okay. What's going on?\Nううん どうしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:29.51,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Um... I really wanted to \Nsee you both and talk.\Nあの どうしても会ってお話したくて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:34.08,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,So...\Nあのね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:40.35,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,I want to try out for the \N{\i1}Apricot{\i0} audition, too.\Nプリコットのオーディション 私も 受けたい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:54.97,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,You probably guessed... {\i1}Apricot{\i0} is a \Nmagazine I've always admired.\Nわかっちゃってるよね アプリコットは本当は私の すごく憧れの雑誌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:12:02.41,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,That's why, as a devoted reader, my honest \Nwish is for Amana-chan to win, but....\Nだからアマナちゃんに勝ってほしいのは 愛読者としての本当の気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:03.21,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,That's why, as a devoted reader, my honest \Nwish is for Amana-chan to win, but....\Nでも
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:08.12,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,It's also true that I can't just \Nsit back and watch... I'm sorry.\N見てるだけじゃいられないのも本当なの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.24,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,It's also true that I can't just \Nsit back and watch... I'm sorry.\Nごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:16.65,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,If I stay like this, I won't \Nbe able to truly support you.\Nこのままじゃ私 天菜ちゃんをちゃんと応援できない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:21.76,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,So I realized I want to enter,\N for my own sake.\Nだから 私は私のために出たいって思って
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:28.81,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Please... Amana-chan.\Nお願いします 天菜ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:43.01,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Yes! Of course... absolutely!\Nうん そんなのもちろんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.48,0:12:45.84,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,I'll have to give it everything I've got!\Nアマナ 頑張らなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:58.88,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,I think it's jealousy... \NEven I am surprised by it.\N嫉妬…だと思うの 自分でも驚いちゃうけど
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:04.28,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,I {\i1}know{\i0} it is... \NI just love that magazine, that's all...\N分かってるの 私はただ好きってだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:08.12,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,it's not like I could make \Nthat world any more beautiful.\N私があの世界を素敵にできるわけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:16.11,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,If Amana-chan were the cover girl,\N I'd still be absolutely thrilled.\N天菜ちゃんがカバーガールだったら私 絶対ときめくもん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.86,SC_Bottom,叶月,0,0,0,,So, which one would you {\i1}really{\i0} prefer?\Nもうどっちなの?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:23.83,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,It's truly both.\Nどっちもホントなの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:30.24,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,So, in a way...\Nだから なんていうか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:35.20,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Auditioning is really \Njust to satisfy myself.\N私がオーディションを受けるのは ただの自己満足
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:38.51,SC_Bottom,叶月,0,0,0,,But that's not the only reason, is it?\Nだけでもないんじゃない?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:43.65,SC_Bottom,叶月,0,0,0,,If jealousy is going to create issues,\N嫉妬のせいで迷惑かけちゃうくらいなら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:46.93,SC_Bottom,叶月,0,0,0,,wouldn't it be better to show \Nyour support by competing openly?\N堂々と戦うことで応援したい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:49.97,SC_Bottom,叶月,0,0,0,,Right?\Nでしょ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:58.19,SC_Bottom,叶月,0,0,0,,Give it your best, Alstroemeria!\N頑張れ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:13:59.76,SC_Bottom,叶月,0,0,0,,Give it your best, Alstroemeria!\Nアルストロメリア
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:05.75,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,You know, I don't have much confidence...\Nアマナね 全然自信なくて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:10.70,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,When I said, "I'll do my best," the \Ntruth is... it's kind of the opposite.\N頑張らなくちゃって言ったのは本当は 反対
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:13.59,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Maybe it's the same for both of us, but...\N二人ともかもだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:17.12,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,there's a chance only one \Nof us will be chosen, right?\Nどっちかだけ選ばれないことだってあるよね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:20.71,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,If that happens, we might not be \Nable to be like we were before...\Nそうなったら 今までみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:29.51,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,If...\Nもし
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:34.94,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,If you're really worried... \Nthen you don't have to enter!\Nもし心配だったら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:37.19,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,If you're really worried... \Nthen you don't have to enter!\Nで でなくていいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:42.25,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,But... if you do enter, \Nyou have to give it your all.\Nで 出るなら全力 出さなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:46.49,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I think Chiyuki-san \Nwill too... for sure...\Nうん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:49.21,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I think Chiyuki-san \Nwill too... for sure...\N千雪さんもきっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:54.51,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,But, because\Nでも だから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:57.75,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,we're both giving it our best...\N全力だから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:01.93,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,I'm scared of what will happen \Nif one of us loses.\N負けた時が怖いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:13.05,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Producer!\Nプロデューサーさん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:15.52,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I...\Nごめんなさい あまな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:18.39,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,I'm withdrawing from the audition!\Nオーディションを辞退します
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:19.69,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Amana-chan!\Nあまなちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:24.56,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,I gave it a lot of thought.\Nアマナね いっぱい考えたの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.10,0:15:28.28,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,I want to support Chiyuki-san! \NShe's the one who truly suits {\i1}Apricot{\i0}!\Nアマナ チユキさんを応援したい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:30.95,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,I want to support Chiyuki-san! \NShe's the one who truly suits {\i1}Apricot{\i0}!\Nアプリコットにぴったりなの チユキさんなんだもん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.52,0:15:37.33,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,I know that, and yet...\N I don't even know how to \Ngive it my best anymore...\Nそれが分かってるのに どうやって頑張ったらいいのか分からないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:42.46,SC_Bottom,制作人,0,0,0,,Amana, could you hear me out—?\Nアマナ、聞いてくれるか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:48.86,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry! I know doing something \Nlike this is causing a lot of trouble...\Nごめんなさい すっごく すっごく迷惑かかっちゃうよね こんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:54.83,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,But going into the audition with \Nthese feelings isn't right either!\Nでも こんな風に思いながら出場するの もっと良くないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:15:58.81,SC_Bottom,制作人,0,0,0,,Amana...\Nアマナ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.85,0:16:08.55,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,I'll withdraw from the audition.\N私がエントリーを取りやめます
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:10.44,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Ch-Chiyuki-san...\Nち ちえきさん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.91,0:16:16.31,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,This is my fault. I... didn't \Nunderstand anything.\N私のせいです 私 何にも分かってなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:21.84,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,I had convinced myself that Amana-chan \Nwould win the Grand Prix...\Nあまなちゃんがグランプリになるってどこかで信じ込んでて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:27.00,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,I thought I understood what it meant to \Ntruly compete and how Amana-chan felt,\N本当に勝負するっていうことも 天菜ちゃんのことも
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:30.00,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,but I really didn't.\N分かってるつもりで全然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.92,0:16:37.67,SC_Bottom,制作人,0,0,0,,I understand how both of you feel.\N二人の気持ちは分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.32,0:16:43.13,SC_Bottom,制作人,0,0,0,,But I called you here today because \Nthere's something I need to tell you.\Nでもな 今日呼んだのは伝えなきゃいけないことがあるからなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:46.09,SC_Bottom,制作人,0,0,0,,The truth is, for this audition...\Nこのオーディション
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:49.84,SC_Bottom,制作人,0,0,0,,Amana has already been selected \Nas the Grand Prix winner.\N天野のグランプリが内定した
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:56.35,SC_Bottom,制作人,0,0,0,,I thought your decision to enter the \Naudition was admirable, Chiyuki.\Nオーディションに出るって決断 俺はすごいと思った
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:59.38,SC_Bottom,制作人,0,0,0,,But... the Grand Prix won't be yours.\Nでも グランプリは千雪じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:03.23,SC_Bottom,制作人,0,0,0,,I want you to think about whether there's \Nstill a reason for you to compete.\Nそれでも出場する理由があるのか 考えてほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.06,0:17:07.63,SC_Bottom,制作人,0,0,0,,I'm not fond of handling \Nthings this way, either.\N俺もこういうやり方は好きじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:12.58,SC_Bottom,制作人,0,0,0,,But the client made this decision after \Nevaluating Amana's past activities.\Nでも 先方がアマナのこれまでの活動を評価して 決めたことなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:17.28,SC_Bottom,制作人,0,0,0,,I'll respect Amana's choice \Nabout whether or not to withdraw.\N辞退するかは アマナの意見を尊重する
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:22.05,SC_Bottom,制作人,0,0,0,,No matter what decision you make, \NI'll support you both fully.\Nどんな結論を出したとしても 全力でサポートする
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:23.88,SC_Bottom,制作人,0,0,0,,So...\Nだから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:28.28,SC_Bottom,制作人,0,0,0,,I want you to think hard about \Nwhat's truly most important to you.\N何が自分にとって 一番大事なのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:29.86,SC_Bottom,制作人,0,0,0,,I want you to think hard about \Nwhat's truly most important to you.\Nもう一回考えてみてほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:34.15,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,For me...\N私にとって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.15,0:17:38.17,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,The most... important thing...\N一番 大事なこと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:48.69,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,How about we walk a little \Nmore before heading back?\Nもうちょっと歩いてから帰らない?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:52.44,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,Yeah...\Nうん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:02.97,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,When the three of us are together, \Nour voices are unbeatable!\N3人そろったら 最強の声だね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:05.61,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,My voice... no, I can't hear it... \Nit's like it won't come out.\N声…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:09.24,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,My voice... no, I can't hear it... \Nit's like it won't come out.\Nううん 聞こえないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:10.62,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,My voice... no, I can't hear it... \Nit's like it won't come out.\N出てないみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:17.25,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,She's the one who truly suits {\i1}Apricot{\i0}!\Nアプリコットにぴったりなの 千雪さんなんだもん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:26.67,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,\Nあー
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:31.33,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,\Nあーー
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:35.25,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Chiyuki-san?\Nちゆきさん?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:49.67,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,I used to practice vocal \Nexercises here a lot.\Nあたし 前はよくここで発声練習してて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:53.78,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,\N补
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.78,0:18:57.12,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,\N补
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:02.25,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,It seems like my voice still \Nisn't coming out properly...\Nまだ喉が開いてないみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:06.82,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,M-Me too...\Nて てんかも
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:10.87,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,\N补
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:15.57,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,\N补
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.06,0:19:19.14,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Ch-Chiyuki-san! Um...\Nち 千雪さん あの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:26.64,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,I... I...\Nあ あの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:28.17,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Yes...\Nうん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:38.30,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,S-sorry, it looks like I'm \Nlosing my voice too...\Nご ごめん あまなもちょっと出ないみたい 声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:42.20,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Amana-chan...\N天ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:50.89,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Hey...\Nねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.68,0:19:59.65,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,How about we play the \N"Game of Opposites" again?\N反対ごっこ しよっか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.88,0:20:15.98,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Amana-chan! I hope you fail the audition!\Nあまなちゃん オーディション落ちたらいいのにー
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:22.49,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Let your voice out! All right, \NAmana-chan, it's your turn!\Nっ出していいの声
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:25.45,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,Let your voice out! All right, \NAmana-chan, it's your turn!\Nはい アマナちゃんの番
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.38,0:20:37.88,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,I hope both of you fail the audition!\N二人とも オーディション落ちたらいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:45.27,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,Na-chan! It's okay if you lose!\Nなーちゃん 負けてもいいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:51.02,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,If you lose, it'll... destroy \Nwhat's most important!\N負ければ こわれちゃうから 大事なもの!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.06,0:21:10.66,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Chiyuki-san! I hope you fail the audition!\Nちゆきさん オーディション 落ちればいいのにー
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:19.71,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,I really, really, really hope you fail!\Nちゆきさんが 絶対 絶対絶対 落ちればいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:24.33,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,Both of you... fail!\N2人とも 落ちて!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:31.01,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,I want to lose!\N負けた——い!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:35.94,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,I want to lose, too!\N天野も 負けた——い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:43.32,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,Both of you... lose!\N2人とも 負けて——
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.39,0:21:51.46,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,And... I absolutely hate Alstroemeria!\Nもう アルストロメリアなんか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.46,0:21:52.65,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,And... I absolutely hate Alstroemeria!\N大っきらい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:58.46,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,Alstroemeria is... not what's most important!\Nアルストロメリア なんか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:02.38,SC_Bottom,甜花,0,0,0,,Alstroemeria is... not what's most important!\N一番 大事じゃ ない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.38,0:22:09.52,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Alstroemeria is... Alstroemeria is...\Nアルストロメリアなんか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.52,0:22:13.25,SC_Bottom,甘奈,0,0,0,,Alstroemeria is... Alstroemeria is...\Nアルストロメリア なんか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.04,0:22:19.36,SC_Bottom,千雪,0,0,0,,... is something I hate, and \Nit's not what's most important.\N大っきらいだし 一番大事じゃない
